title: All Saints Day - Breaking the Tide ( 2013 EP )
description:
All Saints Day - Breaking the Tide

genre: alternative rock

Track list:

1. Feels Good

2. Fingers

3. Hold Fast

4. Its Just Us ( but at least the whiskey is sweet )

5. Last Few Breaths


This EP is brought to you by a local Colorado band from Denver. The CD was made just recently in 2013.  The CD is available on Itunes, Google play store, Iphone store.  Its 5$ for album or 99cents per song. If you enjoy the CD please go support the band and purchase a song or the album.

Join the bands forum and follow the band at http://allsaintsdayrocks.com

Ask any question about the band, follow there gigs, and remember August 16th 2013 is the EP release party.  If your in Denver or in the area,  show the band some love and attend and rock out to some good local music.
